longBusinessSummary: YOC AG provides mobile advertising technology solutions in Germany, Austria, and Poland. The company develops digital advertising formats for automated trading through its marketplace. Its products include VIS.X, a go-to-platform for programmatic advertising; YOC Inline Video Ad for sharing messages across display and video placements; and YOC Understitial Ad, a user initiated format that allows the individual to reveal the ad by scrolling up or down. The company also provides YOC Mystery Ad, an advertising format, which allows users to interact directly with the campaign; YOC Mystery Scroller, a reactive-scroll technology that enables users to interact with advertising message; YOC Ads Plus, which provides various product variations; and YOC Branded Takeover that offers a combination of various formats. YOC AG was founded in 2001 and is headquartered in Berlin, Germany.
